    <item>
      <title>北约负责人说，俄罗斯的关系应恢复战争后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/nato-chief-says-russia-relations-should-be-restored-after-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约秘书长马克·鲁特（Mark Rutte）表示，一旦乌克兰的战斗结束，与俄罗斯的关系最终应归一化，同时强调需要对莫斯科保持压力，以确保停火谈判的进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/nato-chief-says-russia-relations-should-be-restored-after-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 12:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯说，它能够释放以色列人质，四个尸体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯说，它愿意释放一个活着的美国人质和来自加沙的其他双重国民的四个尸体，该组织表示将提高停火谈判的惊喜举动，尽管以色列对此表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京要求我们特使在谈话后向特朗普传达信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/moscow-targeted-in-drone-attack-after-us-envoy-s-visit-to-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫说，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）要求在与莫斯科的美国特使史蒂夫·维特科夫（Steve Witkoff）进行深夜对话中，向美国唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）传达信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/moscow-targeted-in-drone-attack-after-us-envoy-s-visit-to-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 08:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>我们在寻求停火时悄悄地收紧俄罗斯制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-quietly-tightens-russia-sanctions-as-it-seeks-ceasefire-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在通过限制能源付款来收紧对俄罗斯的制裁，即使它与总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）就乌克兰战争进行了和平谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-quietly-tightens-russia-sanctions-as-it-seeks-ceasefire-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默（Schumer）撤退了关闭威胁，增强了比尔的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/schumer-signals-he-won-t-block-gop-bill-to-avert-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）有两种选择，因为时钟到政府资助截止日期：放弃他的威胁以阻止共和党法案或迫使3月15日的破坏性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/schumer-signals-he-won-t-block-gop-bill-to-avert-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:30:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
